{
  "page": "Alleras",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Alleras<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Sphinx</span></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Alleras_by_eldritch-historian.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Alleras by eldritch-historian.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3e/Alleras_by_eldritch-historian.png/350px-Alleras_by_eldritch-historian.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"383\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3e/Alleras_by_eldritch-historian.png/525px-Alleras_by_eldritch-historian.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3e/Alleras_by_eldritch-historian.png/700px-Alleras_by_eldritch-historian.png 2x\" /></a><div>Alleras the Sphinx, by eldritch-historian ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nThe Sphinx<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Acolyte\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Acolyte\">Acolyte</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Race</th><td>\nMixed <small>(half-<a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornish</a>, half-<a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Islander</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornish</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafalleras.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafalleras.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Alleras</b>, known as the <b>Sphinx</b>, is an <a href=\"/index.php/Acolyte\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Acolyte\">acolyte</a> studying at the <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> His mother is a <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Islander</a> trader, and he claims not to be a <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lord</a>'s son, despite the claims of a few others.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes_by_Alleras\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes by Alleras</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes_about_Alleras\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes about Alleras</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Theories\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Theories</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alleras&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_Alleras\" title=\"Category:Images of Alleras\">Images of Alleras</a></div>\n<p>Alleras is slender, comely, and has a soft smile.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> He has curly black hair, a widow's peak, and big black eyes like <a href=\"/index.php/Onyx\" title=\"Onyx\">onyx</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Alleras has skin the color of teak<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> or a light brown <a href=\"/index.php/Ale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ale\">ale</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> The youth usually wears doeskin breeches, and a snug green brigandine with <a href=\"/index.php/Iron\" title=\"Iron\">iron</a> studs.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> He speaks with a soft <a href=\"/index.php/Dornish\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dornish\">Dornish</a> drawl.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Alleras prefers the sweet <a href=\"/index.php/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">wines</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Isles</a> rather than of those of <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> He displays remarkable skill with his <a href=\"/index.php/Goldenheart\" title=\"Goldenheart\">goldenheart</a> longbow, also from the <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Isles</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Alleras is in a circle of friends that includes <a href=\"/index.php/Armen\" title=\"Armen\">Armen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Pate_(novice)\" title=\"Pate (novice)\">Pate</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Mollander\" title=\"Mollander\">Mollander</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Roone\" title=\"Roone\">Roone</a>. He does not consider their fellow novice <a href=\"/index.php/Leo_Tyrell_(son_of_Moryn)\" title=\"Leo Tyrell (son of Moryn)\">Leo Tyrell</a> to be a friend.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Alleras is doted on by the serving wenches of the <a href=\"/index.php/Quill_and_Tankard\" title=\"Quill and Tankard\">Quill and Tankard</a>, including <a href=\"/index.php/Rosey\" title=\"Rosey\">Rosey</a>, which makes Pate jealous.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alleras&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Alleras has a <a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishman</a> for a father and a <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Islander</a> for a mother.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> He has been at the <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a> for a year, and has forged three links in his <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">maester</a>'s chain, the most recent of which is <a href=\"/index.php/Copper\" title=\"Copper\">copper</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> At some point in their time at the Citadel, Leo Tyrell gave Alleras the nickname \"Sphinx\", as he was \"a bit of this, a bit of that\", like a <a href=\"/index.php/Sphinx\" title=\"Sphinx\">sphinx</a> is made of multiple creatures.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-11\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alleras&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alleras&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Alleras_by_Dallas_Williams_(detail).jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/09/Alleras_by_Dallas_Williams_%28detail%29.jpg/350px-Alleras_by_Dallas_Williams_%28detail%29.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/0/09/Alleras_by_Dallas_Williams_%28detail%29.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Alleras_by_Dallas_Williams_(detail).jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Alleras and a <a href=\"/index.php/Glass_candle\" title=\"Glass candle\">glass candle</a>, by Dallas Williams © FFG</div></div></div>\n<p>Having forged his copper link, Alleras celebrates at the <a href=\"/index.php/Quill_and_Tankard\" title=\"Quill and Tankard\">Quill and Tankard</a> by purchasing drinks for his friends. He practices his archery skills by shooting at apples thrown above the <a href=\"/index.php/Honeywine\" title=\"Honeywine\">Honeywine</a> by <a href=\"/index.php/Mollander\" title=\"Mollander\">Mollander</a>. Alleras strikes them all, except for the last apple which he allows to fall into the river untouched, as he believes the day you make them all, you stop improving. He and his friends speak of rumors of <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragons</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>, and Alleras tells them that <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> is still alive, and that \"the dragon has three heads\". <a href=\"/index.php/Leo_Tyrell_(son_of_Moryn)\" title=\"Leo Tyrell (son of Moryn)\">Leo Tyrell</a> arrives at the inn, and insults the companions while confirming Alleras's story, and informing them that there is a <a href=\"/index.php/Glass_candle\" title=\"Glass candle\">glass candle</a> burning in <a href=\"/index.php/Archmaester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Archmaester\">Archmaester</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Marwyn\" title=\"Marwyn\">Marwyn</a>'s chambers. The friends decide to head back to the Citadel to retire for the evening, except for <a href=\"/index.php/Pate_(novice)\" title=\"Pate (novice)\">Pate</a> who is left with Leo. Before he goes, Alleras reassures Pate that if Leo does not have the <a href=\"/index.php/Coin\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Coin\">coin</a> to buy wine, he cannot afford <a href=\"/index.php/Rosey\" title=\"Rosey\">Rosey</a> either.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-12\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Via a glass candle, Archmaester Marwyn <a href=\"/index.php/Prophecy\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Prophecy\">foresees</a> the arrival in <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Tarly\" title=\"Samwell Tarly\">Samwell Tarly</a>, and sends Alleras to the <a href=\"/index.php/Seneschal%27s_Court\" title=\"Seneschal&#39;s Court\">Seneschal's Court</a> to meet him. After Sam tells his story to Alleras — including the fact that his traveling companion, <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">Maester</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Maekar_I)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Maekar I)\">Aemon</a>, mysteriously spoke that \"the <a href=\"/index.php/Sphinx\" title=\"Sphinx\">sphinx</a> is the riddle, not the riddler\", before his death — the Sphinx brings him to Marwyn at the <a href=\"/index.php/Ravenry\" title=\"Ravenry\">Ravenry</a>. Maester Aemon believed that <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> was the <a href=\"/index.php/Prince_that_was_promised\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Prince that was promised\">prince that was promised</a>, and must be taught and protected by a maester; but since Aemon died on the way to Oldtown, Marwyn decides to sail to find her in <a href=\"/index.php/Slaver%27s_Bay\" title=\"Slaver&#39;s Bay\">Slaver's Bay</a>. The archmaester tasks Alleras with looking after Sam.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_by_Alleras\">Quotes by Alleras</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alleras&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes by Alleras\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Alleras_by_elalendi.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1f/Alleras_by_elalendi.png/350px-Alleras_by_elalendi.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"527\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/1/1f/Alleras_by_elalendi.png 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Alleras_by_elalendi.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Alleras the Sphinx, by elalendi ©</div></div></div>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Roone</b>: You always miss your last shot. See?<br />\n<b>Alleras</b>: The day you make them all is the day you stop improving.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-13\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Roone\" title=\"Roone\">Roone</a> and Alleras</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Leo</b>: I understand you won your <a href=\"/index.php/Copper\" title=\"Copper\">copper</a> link. I'll drink to that.<br />\n</p><p><b>Alleras</b>: I only buy for friends. And I am no <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lord</a>'s son, I've told you that. My mother was a trader.<br />\n</p>\n<b>Leo</b>: Your mother was a <a href=\"/index.php/Monkey\" title=\"Monkey\">monkey</a> from the <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Isles</a>. The <a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornish</a> will fuck anything with a hole between its legs. Meaning no offense. You may be brown as a nut, but at least you bathe.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-14\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Leo_Tyrell_(son_of_Moryn)\" title=\"Leo Tyrell (son of Moryn)\">Leo Tyrell</a> and Alleras</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>You shame <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">your House</a> with every word you say. You shame the <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a> by being one of us.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-15\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Alleras, to <a href=\"/index.php/Leo_Tyrell_(son_of_Moryn)\" title=\"Leo Tyrell (son of Moryn)\">Leo Tyrell</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Samwell</b>: Are you a <a href=\"/index.php/Novice\" title=\"Novice\">novice</a>?<br />\n</p><p><b>Alleras</b>: An <a href=\"/index.php/Acolyte\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Acolyte\">acolyte</a>. Alleras, by some called Sphinx.<br />\n<b>Samwell</b>: The <a href=\"/index.php/Sphinx\" title=\"Sphinx\">sphinx</a> is the riddle, not the riddler. Do you know what that means?<br />\n<b>Alleras</b>: No. Is it a riddle?<br />\n</p>\n<b>Samwell</b>: I wish I knew.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Tarly\" title=\"Samwell Tarly\">Samwell Tarly</a> and Alleras</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_about_Alleras\">Quotes about Alleras</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alleras&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes about Alleras\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Sarella_Sand_by_NyanmiEuphoriA.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/82/Sarella_Sand_by_NyanmiEuphoriA.jpg/350px-Sarella_Sand_by_NyanmiEuphoriA.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/82/Sarella_Sand_by_NyanmiEuphoriA.jpg/525px-Sarella_Sand_by_NyanmiEuphoriA.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/82/Sarella_Sand_by_NyanmiEuphoriA.jpg/700px-Sarella_Sand_by_NyanmiEuphoriA.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Sarella_Sand_by_NyanmiEuphoriA.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Alleras by Nyanmi EuphoriA ©</div></div></div>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>It had been <a href=\"/index.php/Leo_Tyrell_(son_of_Moryn)\" title=\"Leo Tyrell (son of Moryn)\">Lazy Leo</a> who dubbed Alleras \"the Sphinx.\" A <a href=\"/index.php/Sphinx\" title=\"Sphinx\">sphinx</a> is a bit of this, a bit of that: a human face, the body of a <a href=\"/index.php/Lion\" title=\"Lion\">lion</a>, the wings of a hawk. Alleras was the same: his father was a <a href=\"/index.php/Dornishman\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dornishman\">Dornishman</a>, his mother a black-skinned <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Islander</a>. His own skin was dark as teak. And like the green <a href=\"/index.php/Marble\" title=\"Marble\">marble</a> sphinxes that flanked the <a href=\"/index.php/Citadel\" title=\"Citadel\">Citadel</a>'s main gate, Alleras had eyes of <a href=\"/index.php/Onyx\" title=\"Onyx\">onyx</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-16\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Pate_(novice)\" title=\"Pate (novice)\">Pate</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The Sphinx was always smiling, as if he knew some secret jape.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-17\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Pate_(novice)\" title=\"Pate (novice)\">Pate</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Theories\">Theories</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alleras&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Theories\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">Main article: <a href=\"/index.php/Alleras/Theories\" title=\"Alleras/Theories\">Alleras/Theories</a></div>\n<p>Evidence suggests that Alleras may be a disguised <a href=\"/index.php/Sarella_Sand\" title=\"Sarella Sand\">Sarella Sand</a>, one of <a href=\"/index.php/Oberyn_Martell\" title=\"Oberyn Martell\">Oberyn Martell</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> daughters known as the <a href=\"/index.php/Sand_Snakes\" title=\"Sand Snakes\">Sand Snakes</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Alleras&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.00</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.01</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.02</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.03</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.04</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\">1.05</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\">1.06</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\">1.07</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\">1.08</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-9\">1.09</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-10\">1.10</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-11\">1.11</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-12\">1.12</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-13\">1.13</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-14\">1.14</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-15\">1.15</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-16\">1.16</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-17\">1.17</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Prologue\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Prologue\">Prologue</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafalleras.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafalleras.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Alleras.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Appendix\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">4.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\">4.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\">4.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-3\">4.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-4\">4.4</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_45\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 45\">Chapter 45</a>, Samwell V.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.towerofthehand.com/blog/2010/08/24_if_its_chains_you_want_/index.html\">If It's Chains You Want, Come With Me</a>, Tower of the Hand</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403181426\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.135 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.371 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1787/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 11599/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 16464/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 3701/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 8291/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.220/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.44 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  344.621      1 -total\n 86.81%  299.151      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 86.29%  297.361      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.98%   37.852     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  8.99%   30.966     25 